{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>在线性代数、计算几何中，向量点积是一种十分重要的运算。给定两个$n$维向量$a=(a_1,a_2,...,a_n)$和$b=(b_1,b_2,...,b_n)$，求点积$a·b=a_1b_1+a_2b_2+...+a_nb_n$。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"向量点积计算 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>一个整数，即两个向量的点积结果。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行是一个整数$n(1≤n≤1000)$；<p><p>第二行包含n个整数$a_1,a_2,...,a_n$；<p><p>第三行包含n个整数$b_1,b_2,...,b_n$；<p><p>相邻整数之间用单个空格隔开。每个整数的绝对值都不超过$1000$。<p>","examples":"<input>3\n1 4 6\n2 1 5\n</input><output>36\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1108","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}